"StayHere: WebPage Bookmark" Is an *Easy To Use* tool that will let you save you current position in a web page 📖 and return to this position at any time.

it is a MUST HAVE to any Online Reader.

all the data is stored in your google account so it *Sync's with all your devices*📱💻 and locally so only you have access to it 🔐🔐.

Feel free to Contact me if you have any questions or suggestions😉😉.
